snippet.title: Absolute Proof Sandy Hook Soto's Classroom Staged for Photos, Inside and Out.  Changed

localized.description:
This is absolute Proof they staged Sandy Hook Soto's classroom.  Depending on if they were taking inside or outside photos.  

I show pictures from the night of the shooting, the day after, the inside of Soto's classroom.  They are all different. 

If they stage one classroom for 'crime' photos and change it, then that proves the whole thing was staged and a hoax.  

Update - 3/5/14 - Official Timeline does not match Police Dash Cam Video of children being evacuated. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7qFEsXAipaM

http://sherriequestioningall.blogspot.com/2014/03/absolute-proof-sandy-hook-sotos.html
